# SOP-MET-004

## Feature Filtering, Quality Control and Normalization of Untargeted LC-MS Data

### Overview

This SOP describes the filtering and normalization workflow applied after data import and initial quality control (SOP-MET-003).

The workflow includes:

* blank filtering;
* QC stability filtering;
* feature filtering summary;
* missing value imputation;
* total signal normalization;
* log transformation;
* PCA before and after normalization;
* export of the final analysis matrix.

The objective is to reduce analytical noise, remove unstable features and prepare the dataset for downstream statistical analyses.

