## Parameter Justification

| Parameter                | Value                         |
| ------------------------ | ----------------------------- |
| Sample/Blank Ratio       | > 5                           |
| QC RSD                   | < 30%                         |
| Missing Value Imputation | Half-min                      |
| Normalization            | Total Signal Normalization    |
| Transformation           | log10(x + 1e-6)               |
| QC Type                  | Pooled QC                     |
| PCA Scaling              | Unit Variance (`scale.=TRUE`) |

These parameters were selected based on common practices in untargeted LC-MS metabolomics and the recommendations discussed during metabolomics training and coursework.

